Description:
Superbly Renovated Lifestyle Property
A stunning renovation allows you to move in with nothing left to do! Set on approximately two acres of land, the residence maintains the period features of Murray Pine flooring and 12 foot ceilings added to all the modern conveniences we have come to enjoy.
~ Dream kitchen with Bosch appliances, dishwasher, walk in pantry, massive island bench and cafe windows to entertaining area.
~ Enclosed, undercover entertaining area with built in BBQ, rangehood, benches and power.
~ Open plan dining and living room with built in cupboards, ceiling fans and doors opening to the verandah.
~ Three generous carpeted bedrooms, all with built in robes and ceiling fans, and main with French doors to front verandah.
~ Separate office/study with built in desk and cupboards.
~ Walk in storage room plus hallway linen storage.
~ Luxurious bathroom with bath and large shower recess.
~ Massive laundry with two troughs, Robinhood ironing centre, cupboards, benches and a second separate toilet.
~ Ducted reverse cycle heating and cooling.
~ 18 solar panels.
~ Double carport with lock up storage, workshop and outside toilet.
~ Garden shed.
~ Excellent bore.
~ Automatic, computerised watering system.
~ Three good paddocks, two with water troughs and shelters.
~ Located on a sealed road and handy to Cobram.
Everything has been thought of in this lovely home. Call our office to arrange your inspection now!

Description:
DESIGN, SIZE, MURRAY RIVER
This impressive architect designed tri level home is seeking a new owner who desires something different and is prepared to put their own special touch on this wonderfully unique home. There is everything to offer those with a young family to keep them entertained, the Murray River, the hugely popular Thompsons Beach and the bush backdrop which abounds with native birdlife. Views from the balcony accessed from the living room and kitchen meals area are stunning, while downstairs the huge rumpus room complete with fantastic wood fuelled fire warms both upstairs and downstairs living areas. Accommodation includes 3 bedrooms plus a separate study, the master bedroom comprises a WIR and ensuite bathroom. Additionally there is a fitted wine cellar that would suit the discerning collector. This home impresses with its design, size and prime location. Call today for an appointment to inspect.
